13
00:01:55,453 --> 00:01:57,334
both TCM Acupuncture

14
00:01:57,453 --> 00:01:58,814
and brewing medicine.

15
00:01:59,094 --> 00:02:00,693
Mr Zheng, you don't
need to worry at all.

16
00:02:04,494 --> 00:02:05,389
Mr Ren,

17
