200
00:10:27,374 --> 00:10:28,814
Make some porridge for her.

201
00:10:28,814 --> 00:10:29,814
Make it

202
00:10:30,013 --> 00:10:31,054
with rice bran oil.

203
00:10:31,254 --> 00:10:32,333
